Tiramisu

Indulge in the rich, creamy deliciousness of our homemade tiramisu! Made with layers of fluffy mascarpone, sponge cake and espresso-soaked ladyfingers, and dusted with cocoa powder, this classic Italian dessert is the perfect ending to any meal or a sweet treat any time of day.

Cheese Cake

Satisfy your sweet tooth with our delectable homemade cheesecake! Made with a buttery graham cracker crust, creamy cheesecake filling and topped with fresh fruit or homemade compote, this classic dessert is the perfect balance of sweet and tangy. Indulge in a slice or take a whole cake to share with your loved ones. Available now at our cookie shop

Birtish Shorthair

The British Shorthair is the pedigreed version of the traditional British domestic cat, with a distinctively stocky body, dense coat, and broad face. The most familiar colour variant is the "British Blue", with a solid grey-blue coat, orange eyes, and a medium-sized tail.
